        h1 Please Input the Book's ID
        form(action="/delete1" method="POST" class="form-search")
            div(class="input-group input-group-lg" id="searchgroup")
                input(type="text" value="" name="ID" placeholder="input the ID" class="form-control")
                span(class="input-group-btn")
                    button(type="submit" class="btn btn-lg btn-primary") GO!